caption.p:
Scheme showing different isolation methods of essential oil from fingered citron fruits. 
   a The average diameter of fruit peel particle is around 2–3 mm; 
   b The absolute pressure in the vacuum is 0.03–0.05 MPa (absolute pressure); 
   c The pore diameter of microfiltration is 0.45 μm; 
   d The molecular weight cut-off (MWCO) of ultrafiltration is 4000 Da.
